TC-AMS-SUBMIT-04

SUMMARY
AMS R1 Submit - Navigating Away Without Submitting Shows Warning Popup with Back to AMS and Continue Options

DESCRIPTION
Verifies that when a farmer or agent has saved all AMS Round 1 responses but has not yet pressed Submit, attempting to navigate away from the AMS screen triggers a warning popup. The popup must inform the user clearly that responses have not been submitted and they must return to submit. Two options must be offered - Back to AMS returns the user to the AMS screen, and Continue proceeds with navigation away. This protects against accidental non-submission.

